    "English": "This long pole forms the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">backbone</span> of a traditional <span class=\"name name-technology\">Autophage staff</span>.<br><br>One of three core components, this can be assembled into a staff at the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Autophage Synthesis Terminal</span> found at all Autophage camps.",
